com.team08storyapp

Class Photo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team08storyapp.Photo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Photo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Photo is a model class representing an image or illustration that can be used in an Annotation on a Story Fragment in a Story or as an illustration on a Story Fragment in a Story. An Photo has the following properties:
    • Photo Id to uniquely identify the Photo.
    • Picture Name is the name the user gave to the Photo.
    • Photo the photo the reader set in the Annotation.
    • Encoded Picture is the Photo encoded for storing it in a file or on a webservice.
    These properties are able to be accessed through the constructor or through public getters/setters.
    Since:
    1.0
